# Cursor Rules (legacy — IEEPIS)

Session protocol lives in `AGENTS.md`. Read it first.

Modern Cursor reads `.cursor/rules/main.mdc` automatically; this `.cursorrules` is the legacy fallback.

Follow the protocol:
1. `.ai/handoff.md` (always)
2. `.ai/memory.md` index → load relevant section
3. For Laravel/Filament code: `.ai/laravel-boost.md`
4. Optional role: `.agents/<role>.md`
